saved_action.name: Tanium - Clean Stale Tanium Client Data
saved_action.comment: Will remove data from Tanium Client directory which is stale, and will safely kill any stale sensor or action processes. Action processes are only terminated when they are run from the Downloads directory.

saved_action.name: Remove Tanium Client Install Files
saved_action.comment: Removes files that may exist due to Client deployment jobs.

saved_action.name: Patch Management - Run Patch Scan
saved_action.comment: Runs a patch scan using the Microsoft Windows Update offline cab file. Scans for patches up to 2 minutes after issue time.

saved_action.name: Patch Management - Install Delivered Patch Files
saved_action.comment: Batch installs all patches that have been deployed to targeted machines.

saved_action.name: Patch Management - Force Patch Scan for Stale Results
saved_action.comment: This package will force a patch scan on machines with results older than 2 days.

saved_action.name: Patch Management - Deploy Patch Scan Files and Scan
saved_action.comment: This action will distribute the latest patch tools to machines that do not have any, or the correct versions, of patch tool files, or are missing the update scan CAB file.

saved_action.name: Patch Management - Deploy Patch Scan Files
saved_action.comment: Deploys an updated version of the Microsoft Windows Update offline patch cab and VBScript files needed for patch scanning to machines with old patch tools.
